com.hazelcast.topic.impl.reliable

Class MessageRunner<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.topic.impl.reliable.MessageRunner<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionCallback<ReadResultSet<ReliableTopicMessage>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientReliableMessageRunner, ReliableMessageRunner

    public abstract class MessageRunner<E>
extends Object
implements ExecutionCallback<ReadResultSet<ReliableTopicMessage>>
    An ExecutionCallback that will try to read an item from the ringbuffer or blocks if no item is available. All data that are read is pushed into the MessageListener. It is a self-perpetuating stream of async calls.

    The runner keeps track of the sequence.
